quran[8{c,v,t}:
3,166,jo nuqsaan larai ke din tumhe pouncha woh Allah ke azan se tha aur is liye tha ke Allah dekh le tum mein se momin kon hain
3,167,"aur munafiq kon, woh munafiq ke jab unn se kaha gaya aao, Allah ki raah mein jung karo ya kam az kam ( apne shehar ki ) mudafat hi karo, to kehnay lagey agar hamein ilm hota ke aaj jung hogi to hum zaroor sath chaltay yeh baat jab woh keh rahay thay uss waqt woh imaan ki nisbat kufar se ziyada qareeb thay woh apni zabanon se woh baatein kehte hain jo un ke dilon mein nahi hoten, aur jo kuch woh dilon mein chupatay hain Allah usay khoob jaanta hai"
3,168,yeh wohi log hain jo khud to baithy rahay o Raan ke jo bhai band larnay gay aur maaray gay un ke mutaliq unhon ne keh diya ke a giroh hamari baat maan letay to nah maaray jatay un se kaho agar tum apne qoul mein sachey ho to khud tumhari mout jab aeye ussay taall kar dikha dena
3,169,"jo log Allah ki raah mein qatal hue hain inhen murda nah samjhoo, woh to haqeeqat mein zindah hain, apne rab ke paas rizaq pa rahay hain"
3,170,"jo kuch Allah ne apne fazl se inhen diya hai uss par khush o Khurram hain, aur mutmaen hain ke jo ahal imaan unkay peechay duniya mein reh gay hain aur abhi wahan nahi puhanche hain un ke liye bhi kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nahi hai"
3,171,woh Allah ke inaam aur is ke fazl par Shadan o Ferhan hain aur un ko maloom ho chuka hai ke Allah mominoun ke ajar ko zaya nahi karta
3,172,jin logon ne zakham khanay ke baad bhi Allah aur rasool ki pukaar par labaik kaha unn mein jo ashkhaas nekokaar aur parhaiz gaar hain unn ke liye bara ajar hai
3,173,"aur woh jin se logon ne kaha ke,"" tumhary khilaaf barri faujein jama hui hain, unn se daro "", to yeh sun kar un ka imaan aur barh gaya aur onhon ne jawab diya ke hamaray liye Allah kaafi hai aur wohi behtareen karsaazay hai"
